\par 100.1. These }{\b Magic}{ rules assume a game between two players. Optional rules allow for more players but aren\rquote t discussed here. These rules can be found at the Wizards of the Coast website at {\*\bkmkstart OLE_LINK7}}{\field{\*\fldinst {\b 
