During the combat phase, from the start of the declare attackers step until the end of the combat phase, the active player\rquote s opponent is the defending player. Creatures can attack only the defending player; they can\rquote 
t attack other players or creatures. During phases other than combat, there is no defending player. See rule 306.3.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {Delayed Triggered Ability
