egeneration or other destruction-replacement effects can replace this action. See rule 419, \'93Replacement and Prevention Effects.\'94
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {Discard
