The source of damage is the object that dealt it. If an effect requires a player to choose a source of damage, he or she may choose either a permanent or a spell on the stack (including one that creates a permanent) or a
ny object referred to by a spell or ability on the stack. A source doesn\rquote t need to be capable of dealing damage to be a legal choice. See rule 419.8, \'93Sources of Damage.\'94
\par 
