ve been used. Permanents untap during their controllers\rquote  untap steps. See also Tap, Untap, and Untapped.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {Target
